@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.29) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.99)) + wp.sin((v2 + 0.21 - tmp + 0.42)))
    v1 = wp.cos(0.96)
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (v0 / 0.95)
